# == Class: cspace_java
#
# Manages the availability of either OpenJDK 7 or the Oracle Java SE (Standard Edition) version 7
# Java Development Kit (JDK), a prerequisite for a CollectionSpace server installation.
#
# === Parameters
#
# Document parameters here.
#
# [*sample_parameter*]
